      "steps": [
        "Place a nonstick pan high heat.",
        "Cut the beef into small pieces.",
        "In a bowl add the beef, salt, pepper, garlic granules and flour. Add 3 tablespoons oil in the pan and saute the beef for 4-5 minutes.",
        "At the same time chop the onions and carrots in large pieces.",
        "Remove the beef from the pan. Add the rest of olive oil, carrots and onions in the pan. Saute until caramelised.",
        "Add the tomato paste, thyme, sugar and the cinnamon sticks in the pan. Mix and saute for a minute.",
        "Deglaze the pot with the wine.",
        "Add the bay leaves, tomato passata, water, beef and cover with the lid, lower the heat to medium, and boil for 2 hours. After 1.5 hours check if more water is needed.",
        "When ready remove from heat. Remove the cinnamon sticks, cloves and bay leaves."
